        "text": "I want to use AIC3101 for capture, so I set enableTVP5158 to false.\n\nI use the cmd as following:\n\naplay -D hw:0,1 -r 16000 -c 2 -f s16_LE /opt/demo.pcm.\n\nThe file of demo.pcm is the data of capture.\n\nThe capture sampleRate is 16K.\n\nIf I set -r to 16K, it can not play normally.\n\nIf I set -r to 8K, it plays slowly."
